  "texts": [
    "Online meetings will be held after the Delphi survey to collect the experts' opinions and optimize and formulate the final checklist.",
    "All opinions and suggestions will be documented, and responses to each expert's suggestions will be provided through email.",
    "After the Delphi survey and virtual consensus meeting, we will refine and optimize the final items included.",
    "Once approved by the experts, we will prepare the manuscript for submission.",
    "After the CHEER checklist is finalized, we will invite authors of medical studies to use it when writing research papers involving GAI tools, simultaneously collecting their opinions and feedback to optimize and improve it."
